184
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:38,480
Keep illness away and reduce disasters.

185
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:44,550
May our people be healthy and safe.

186
00:15:50,730 --> 00:15:51,920
Lady Fan Yun.

187
00:15:52,700 --> 00:15:54,420
